{
  "title": "Pure Energizing Dutch Cashew Pilaf",
  "description": "A hearty and energizing Dutch dish featuring cashews and shio-cure, perfect for a weeknight dinner. This umami-rich pilaf is also nut-free-friendly, making it a great option for those with allergies.",
  "cuisine": "Dutch",
